data.name: Star Jet Alpha
data.detailed_description: Star Jet Alpha is a top-down space shooter inspired by classic arcade games.  Progress through each stage by blowing up enemy space stations while avoiding or destroying enemy missiles, space mines and asteroids.  Unlock Star Jet capabilities by completing stages.
